      "title": "Attempt to set fire to an Eelam refugee",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Eelam refugees have been on a hunger strike for 34 days in a special Trichy camp demanding their release.",
        "In this situation, a refugee named Uma Ramanan has tried to commit suicide by setting himself on fire yesterday (24). However he is saved by all the refugees."
